{
  "text": "The limits of this study include a small sample size preventing statistical evaluation of survey results and the short time period for implementation. The strengths of this study include use of a reliable and valid data collection tool, the Intensice Care Unit Nurse-Physician Questionnaire survey [CITATION_1] .",
  "citation_candidates": [
